00:15:01,390 --> 00:15:02,150
- Baik.
- Ingatlah,

300
00:15:02,150 --> 00:15:03,630
harus selesai
sebelum pukul satu dini hari.

301
00:15:03,840 --> 00:15:04,630
- Cepat.
- Mengerti.

302
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:06,200
Kak? Itu...

303
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:09,080
Tunggu. Kau...

304
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:11,270
Cepatlah.

305
00:15:13,510 --> 00:15:15,320
Berhenti. Apa yang kau lakukan?

306
00:15:16,600 --> 00:15:17,480
Di mana orang-orang kalian?

