00:15:28,390 --> 00:15:29,390
Ada hadiah dari Tuan.

313
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:38,510
Hanya kalian saja?

314
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:41,600
Kau...

315
00:15:50,910 --> 00:15:51,720
Ayo.

316
00:15:56,670 --> 00:15:57,320
Mereka pingsan.

317
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,670
Sungguh.

318
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:04,150
- Kakakku memang hebat.
- Hebat sekali.

319
00:16:04,360 --> 00:16:06,840
Kau memang pendekar wanita. Aku kagum.

320
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:10,150
Ini bukan apa-apa.
Kakakku masih punya jurus lain.

321
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:11,510
Hebat.

322
00:16:11,670 --> 00:16:12,390
Tiga orang bodoh,

323
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:14,080
bertindaklah.

324
00:16:17,390 --> 00:16:18,390
Kalian bertiga, maju.

325
00:16:18,390 --> 00:16:18,750
Maju.

326
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:19,630
- Baik.
- Ayo.

327
00:16:22,550 --> 00:16:26,510
Adik Lingfeng, Saudara Zhuge,
dan Pendekar Wanita Ma,

328
00:16:27,720 --> 00:16:29,720
