344
00:17:08,840 --> 00:17:09,480
Percayalah kepadaku.

345
00:17:09,480 --> 00:17:10,750
- Apa yang kau lakukan?
- Percayalah kepadaku.

346
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:15,640
Di malam gelap, terlihat lampu perahu.

347
00:17:16,510 --> 00:17:19,400
Sebuah cahaya kesepian bersinar.

348
00:17:20,160 --> 00:17:25,830
Kantong garam ada di tangan.
Terima kasih atas bantuan kalian.

349
00:17:31,240 --> 00:17:32,550
Tidak apa-apa, masih ada lagi.

350
00:17:32,590 --> 00:17:34,160
- Garam di tangan...
- Saudara Ye!

351
00:17:35,510 --> 00:17:36,510
Sudah cukup.

352
00:17:37,310 --> 00:17:38,240
Kau sudah kembali?

