391
00:19:31,960 --> 00:19:33,160
Jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama?

392
00:19:34,510 --> 00:19:35,790
Omong kosong.

393
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:39,310
Qing'er menunggunya selama lima tahun,

394
00:19:40,070 --> 00:19:41,310
